# Placement Preparation Journey 🚀

This repository documents my placement preparation journey from **Day 1** until I secure a full-time role.

The goal of this repository is to maintain consistency, track progress, and create a record of everything I learn throughout the placement season.

## Why I Started This Repository

Placement preparation can often feel unstructured and difficult to track. This repository serves as a personal log of my journey, helping me:

* Stay accountable
* Maintain consistency
* Measure progress over time
* Document lessons learned
* Build discipline through daily effort

## Progress Tracking

I plan to update this repository regularly with:

* Daily learning logs
* Completed DSA questions
* New projects
* Interview preparation notes
* Placement milestones

